thread.title: Wall St rockets higher on bull market's birthday

title: Wall St rockets higher on bull market's birthday
text:
Wall St rockets higher on bull market's birthday Friday, March 09, 2018 - 01:28 
The three major indexes shot up more than 1 percent on the bull market's ninth birthday. As Fred Katayama reports, the February jobs report assuaged fears of inflation and aggressive rate hikes.
